  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nHappened after a redirect to www.google.fr from https://imagine.microsoft.com/fr-FR (which occured instantly when prompted the first page). The browser declared the page as \"secure\" although the certificate used was issued to gateway.login.live.com (a Microsoft service)."
